2021/06/07 takeshi:

We will not use 
  CALLBACK_EVENT_SPEECH_READY
  CALLBACK_EVENT_SPEECH_START
  CALLBACK_EVENT_SPEECH_STOP
because these will be called each time the engine detects start/end of speech.

